## Active Jobs Snapshot (2026-04-22)

- Posttrain retries:
  - `3556764`: 4 running (`_2,_3,_4,_5`), 2 failed (`_0,_1`), remaining tasks pending by array limit.
  - `3555102_6`: still running.
